    "body": "## Problem\r\n\r\nvim.fn.writefile() treats Lua strings as Vimscript strings instead of a \"binary clean\" string.\r\n\r\n## Solution:\r\n\r\nTreat Lua-originated strings as blob data.\r\n\r\nRelated (possibly fixes): #35589.\r\n\r\nI looked over #31930 and addressed its review comments here; if this is the version to merge, #31930 should be closed.\r\n",
    "closed_at": "2026-04-22T17:36:43Z",
